Para agregar paquetes al proyecto
```
dotnet add PROJECT_NAME.ccproj || SOLUCTION_NAME package PACKAGE.NAME
```

Agregar el paquete Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.Razor.RunTimeCompilation
para poder tener acutalizada la pagina en tiempo de ejecucion

En start Startup.ConfigureService:
```
services.AddRazorPages().AddRazorRuntimeCompilation();
```

Para conectar dotnet con mysql
```
dotnet add BookListRazor.csproj package Pomelo.EntityFrameworkCore.MySql
```

el paquete oficial de mysql no funciona con la version 3.* de entity EntityFrameworkCore
dotnet ef migrations add MIGRATION_NAME


Add razor page
```
dotnet new page --name index --output Pages/BookList --namespace BookListRazor.Pages.BookList   
```
# Code Generator

Add code generator
```
dotnet tool install -g dotnet-aspnet-codegenerator
```
```
dotnet aspnet-codegenerator [arguments] [-p|--project] [-n|--nuget-package-dir] [-c|--configuration] [-tfm|--target-framework] [-b|--build-base-path] [--no-build] 
dotnet aspnet-codegenerator [-h|--help]
```

add controller
```
dotnet aspnet-codegenerator controller --dataContext ApplicationDbContext -outDir Controllers --controllerName CONTROLLER_NAME --project PROJECT_NAME.csproj
```